This paper proposes a method for target detection and classification problems, which are commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method involves dictionary learning, which is also a popular topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses experiments and results, which may fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
